parameters:
\n<Terra>So, we've successfully tamed the twin beastfolk known as Rui
and Rui.

\n<Terra>So, we've successfully tamed the twin beastfolk known as Rui
and Wanz.

\n<Demon King>Hmm... these twins possess quite interesting magical powers.
They're definitely geniuses with potential for growth.

\n<Demon King>The coagulation crystals are larger than I thought. We've
lost a lot of strength, but this should be enough to make up
for it.

\n<Demon King>Terra. I'd like to praise you for a job well done... well
done indeed.

\n<Terra>Thank you. (So he's the type who believes in praise as
encouragement...)

\n<Latier>Demon Lord, I have taken a liking to Rui as well. May I
please be entrusted with their care?

\n<Megna>Demon Lord! It was Megna who charmed Rui! Despite being
stronger than Megna, now they're totally smitten with me♥

\n<Sheika>It was us who seduced Rui. We've soaked them in pleasure
with our saliva...

\n<Barley>We've made them utterly dependent with our saliva♥ They
can't live without us now♥

\n<Demon King>I had heard that humans are weak to pleasure, but I didn't
expect it to this extent. Since the hero was lecherous, I
decided to change our strategy drastically, and it was the
right choice.
\n<Demon King>All of you, I want to say 'well done'... well done!
\n<Aide>Understood. It will be prepared in bales.

\n<Terra>We don't need rice. Then, leave the education of these two
to us succubi. We'll make sure they become useful.

\n<Demon King>I'm looking forward to it. Also, stop talking to me so
informally, will you?
